Shank's Take:
This blasted rabbit is a nuisance in every meaning of the word. He seems to have some vendetta against me, but that's fair. Seeing someone so superior to you must be frustrating. The fool thinks he can put out my flames of destiny with his water, but he better be prepared to evaporate.

Dagger's Take:
